{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5e737d27aa","title":"紧急呼吁","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bb8eca5ff7","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":26,"articleId":"5e737d27aa","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"ebcd46d792","name":"东方红二中红卫兵"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"814507c672","type":"title","text":"紧急呼吁","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd67de17f0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席教导我们：\"中国的反动分子，靠我们组织起人民去把他打倒。凡是反动的东西，你不打，他就不倒。这也和扫地一样，扫帚不到，灰尘照例不会自己跑掉。\"","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4fbcc5c709","type":"paragraph","text":"目前，有不少散居在街道上的地、富、反、坏、右分子，劳改释放犯，劳动教养解除犯，少年管教释放犯，流氓盗窃分子，投机倒把分子，资本家，伪兵痞，伪警棍，机关、工厂、企业、学校等单位开除除名的这些混蛋们，长期以来厌恶劳动，贪图安逸，成群结队，打架斗殴。经常泡酒馆、茶馆，说坏话，做坏事腐蚀青年，或挑拨离间，造谣生事，或漫骂攻击政府，散布反动言论，严重地危害着首都治安。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e73b79009b","type":"paragraph","text":"严厉警告你们这些社会渣子们，绝不允许你们这些狗崽子继续为非作歹，扰乱社会治安，现在是你们进入垃圾箱的时候了。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc02bb68cc","type":"paragraph","text":"为了保卫党中央，保卫毛主席，我们紧急呼吁：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d63df8f600","type":"paragraph","text":"中共北京新市委、市人委、劳动局、公安局、办事处、派出所和一切有关单位，立即采取措施：","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea1bec4fbd","type":"paragraph","text":"家在农村的，限期还乡生产！","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"48281eb268","type":"paragraph","text":"农村没家的，有关单位立即组织这群混蛋劳动，让他们赶快滚出首都去！","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1df091fc69","type":"paragraph","text":"在这群混蛋没离开北京之前，不管是闲在家里的还是作临时工的，只许规规矩矩，不准乱说乱动，如果乱说乱动，立即予以制裁！","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"786b260024","type":"paragraph","text":"革命造反精神万岁！","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5fd84cf9ea","type":"paragraph","text":"\"扫除一切害人虫，全无敌\"！","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7e499bbd7","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级专政万岁！","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"321e5cf2c5","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党万岁！","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"52c6b6a06c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们最最敬爱的伟大领袖毛主席万岁！万万岁！","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a13569f1e9","type":"paragraph","text":"东方红二中红卫兵","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"68746941d8","type":"paragraph","text":"1966年8月26日","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a459f79a46","type":"paragraph","text":"希望各单位见到通知后立即翻印。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5e737d27aa","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}